---
/**
 * Competitor comparison page — positions Peek above all alternatives.
 */
---

<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Peek vs the Competition — Why We're Different</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Peek vs Wix, Squarespace, Carrd and web agencies. See why 500+ businesses choose Peek for their one-page site." />
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #0b1020;
      --panel: rgba(16, 24, 48, 0.8);
      --panel-strong: #121a33;
      --text: #eef2ff;
      --muted: #a6b0cf;
      --line: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      --accent: #7c9cff;
      --accent2: #67e8f9;
      --success: #86efac;
      --danger: #fca5a5;
      --shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(124,156,255,0.2), transparent 30%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 80% 60%, rgba(103,232,249,0.12), transparent 25%),
        var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
    .container { width: min(1140px, calc(100% - 32px)); margin: 0 auto; }

    /* ─── NAV ─── */
    .nav {
      position: sticky; top: 0;
      backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
      background: rgba(11,16,32,0.75);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
      z-index: 100;
    }
    .nav-inner {
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 16px 0; gap: 16px;
    }
    .brand { font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.2rem; letter-spacing: 0.02em; }
    .brand span { color: var(--accent2); }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 20px; color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.9rem; }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--text); }
    .nav-links a.active { color: var(--accent); }

    /* ─── HERO ─── */
    .hero {
      padding: 90px 0 64px;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
    }
    .hero-glow {
      position: absolute; top: -80px; left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      width: 700px; height: 350px;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(124,156,255,0.22), transparent 70%);
      pointer-events: none;
      animation: glowPulse 5s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    @keyframes glowPulse {
      0%, 100% { opacity: 0.7; transform: translateX(-50%) scale(1); }
      50% { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(-50%) scale(1.08); }
    }

    .hero-badge {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
      padding: 7px 14px; border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(124,156,255,0.3);
      background: rgba(124,156,255,0.1);
      color: var(--accent); font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      animation: fadeUp 0.5s ease-out both;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5.5vw, 5rem);
      line-height: 1.0; letter-spacing: -0.045em;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--text) 35%, var(--accent) 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
      animation: fadeUp 0.5s 0.1s ease-out both;
    }

    .hero p {
      color: var(--muted); font-size: 1.15rem; line-height: 1.7;
      max-width: 62ch; margin: 0 auto 36px;
      animation: fadeUp 0.5s 0.2s ease-out both;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      display: flex; gap: 14px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;
      animation: fadeUp 0.5s 0.3s ease-out both;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 999px;
      border: none; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem;
      transition: all 180ms ease; cursor: pointer;
    }
    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent2));
      color: #07111f; box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(124,156,255,0.4);
    }
    .btn-primary:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 14px 40px rgba(124,156,255,0.5); }
    .btn-ghost {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border: 1px solid var(--line);
      color: var(--text);
    }
    .btn-ghost:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }

    /* ─── COMPARISON TABLE ─── */
    .comparison-section { padding: 64px 0; }
    .comparison-wrap {
      overflow-x: auto;
      border-radius: 24px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.2s ease-out both;
    }

    table {
      width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;
      min-width: 760px;
      font-size: 0.92rem;
    }

    thead th {
      padding: 20px 18px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    }
    thead th:first-child { text-align: left; padding-left: 24px; }

    thead th.peek-col {
      background: rgba(124,156,255,0.1);
      color: var(--accent);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(124,156,255,0.4);
    }

    tbody tr {
      transition: background 150ms ease;
    }
    tbody tr:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); }
    tbody tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }

    tbody td {
      padding: 14px 18px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      text-align: center;
      vertical-align: middle;
    }
    tbody td:first-child {
      text-align: left; padding-left: 24px;
      color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.88rem;
    }
    tbody td:first-child strong { color: var(--text); }

    tbody td.peek-col {
      background: rgba(124,156,255,0.05);
    }

    .check { color: var(--success); font-size: 1.1rem; }
    .cross { color: var(--danger); font-size: 0.95rem; opacity: 0.7; }
    .val { font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem; }
    .val.peek { color: var(--accent); }
    .val.accent { color: var(--accent2); }

    .price-big {
      font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    /* Peek wins column highlight */
    .peek-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 6px;
      background: rgba(124,156,255,0.2);
      color: var(--accent); font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    /* ─── ADVANTAGES ─── */
    .advantages-section { padding: 80px 0; }
    .advantages-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 56px; }
    .section-eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
      font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 14px;
    }
    .section-title {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.2rem);
      letter-spacing: -0.04em; line-height: 1.05; margin-bottom: 14px;
    }
    .section-sub { color: var(--muted); font-size: 1.05rem; max-width: 60ch; line-height: 1.7; }

    .adv-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
    }
    .adv-card {
      padding: 32px 26px;
      background: var(--panel);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 24px;
      transition: all 250ms ease;
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .adv-card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 3px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent), var(--accent2));
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 250ms ease;
    }
    .adv-card:hover {
      border-color: rgba(124,156,255,0.3);
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      box-shadow: 0 24px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
    }
    .adv-card:hover::before { opacity: 1; }

    .adv-num {
      font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: -0.05em;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent2));
      -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
      line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .adv-card h3 {
      font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .adv-card p { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.65; }

    /* ─── SOCIAL PROOF ─── */
    .proof-section { padding: 80px 0; }
    .proof-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 48px; }
    .proof-cities {
      display: flex; gap: 12px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    .city-pill {
      padding: 8px 18px; border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--muted);
    }
    .city-pill span { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 700; }

    .testimonials {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
    }
    .testimonial {
      padding: 28px;
      background: var(--panel);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 20px;
      transition: all 220ms ease;
    }
    .testimonial:hover {
      border-color: rgba(124,156,255,0.25);
      transform: translateY(-3px);
    }
    .stars { color: #fde68a; font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; }
    .testimonial blockquote {
      font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.7;
      color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 18px;
      font-style: normal;
    }
    .testimonial .author {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
    }
    .author-avatar {
      width: 38px; height: 38px; border-radius: 50%;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent2));
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-weight: 800; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #07111f;
    }
    .author-name { font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.88rem; }
    .author-role { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.8rem; }

    /* ─── CTA ─── */
    .cta-section {
      padding: 80px 0;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(124,156,255,0.18), rgba(103,232,249,0.1));
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      text-align: center;
    }
    .cta-section h2 {
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 3rem);
      letter-spacing: -0.04em; margin-bottom: 14px;
    }
    .cta-section > .container > p { color: var(--muted); font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 28px; }

    .email-form {
      display: flex; gap: 12px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;
      max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .email-input {
      flex: 1; min-width: 220px;
      padding: 14px 20px; border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
      color: var(--text); font-size: 0.95rem;
      outline: none; transition: border-color 200ms;
    }
    .email-input::placeholder { color: var(--muted); }
    .email-input:focus { border-color: var(--accent); }

    .guarantee {
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 8px;
      margin-top: 16px; color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.85rem;
    }
    .guarantee svg { color: var(--success); }

    /* ─── FINAL CALLOUT ─── */
    .callout-section { padding: 64px 0; text-align: center; }
    .callout-card {
      padding: 40px;
      background: var(--panel);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 28px;
      max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .callout-card h2 {
      font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.4rem);
      letter-spacing: -0.04em; margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .callout-card p { color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 24px; }

    /* ─── FOOTER ─── */
    footer {
      padding: 40px 0; text-align: center;
      color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.85rem;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    }
    footer a { color: var(--accent); }

    /* ─── REVEAL ─── */
    .reveal { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease; }
    .reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
    .reveal-d1 { transition-delay: 0.1s; }
    .reveal-d2 { transition-delay: 0.2s; }
    .reveal-d3 { transition-delay: 0.3s; }
    .reveal-d4 { transition-delay: 0.4s; }

    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(18px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
    }

    /* ─── RESPONSIVE ─── */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .adv-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .testimonials { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- NAV -->
  <nav class="nav">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="nav-inner">
        <a href="/" class="brand">peek<span>.</span></a>
        <div class="nav-links">
          <a href="/">Home</a>
          <a href="/demos">Demos</a>
          <a href="/vs" class="active">vs Competitors</a>
          <a href="/api/preview?name=Demo">API</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-glow"></div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-badge">Honest Comparison</div>
      <h1>Stop Paying<br/>€500–€5,000<br/>for a Website</h1>
      <p>Get a professional, mobile-first one-page site in 5 minutes — for €59/month. No templates. No drag-and-drop. No agency back-and-forth.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="#get-started" class="btn btn-primary">Get Your Free Preview →</a>
        <a href="#comparison" class="btn btn-ghost">See Full Comparison</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- COMPARISON TABLE -->
  <section class="comparison-section" id="comparison">
    <div class="container">
      <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:40px" class="reveal">
        <div class="section-eyebrow">✦ Feature Comparison</div>
        <h2 class="section-title">How We Stack Up</h2>
        <p class="section-sub">Every other option either costs more, takes longer, or is missing the features that actually matter for local businesses.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="comparison-wrap reveal">
        <table>
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Feature</th>
              <th class="peek-col"><div class="peek-badge">Peek</div><br/><strong style="color:var(--accent)">€59/mo</strong></th>
              <th>Wix</th>
              <th>Squarespace</th>
              <th>Carrd</th>
              <th>Web Agency</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>Price</strong></td>
              <td class="peek-col"><span class="price-big peek">€59</span><br/><span style="color:var(--muted);font-size:0.8rem">/month</span></td>
              <td><span class="price-big">€25</span><br/><span style="color:var(--muted);font-size:0.8rem">/month</span></td>
              <td><span class="price-big">€29</span><br/><span style="color:var(--muted);font-size:0.8rem">/month</span></td>
              <td><span class="price-big val">€19</span><br/><span style="color:var(--muted);font-size:0.8rem">/year</span></td>
              <td><span class="price-big val accent">€500–5K</span><br/><span style="color:var(--muted);font-size:0.8rem">one-time</span></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>Setup time</strong></td>
              <td class="peek-col"><span class="val peek">5 min</span></td>
              <td>2–5 hours</td>
              <td>2–5 hours</td>
              <td>1 hour</td>
              <td>2–8 weeks</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>Auto-generated preview</strong></td>
              <td class="peek-col"><span class="check">✅</span></td>
              <td><span class="cross">❌</span></td>
              <td><span class="cross">❌</span></td>
              <td><span class="cross">❌</span></td>
              <td><span class="cross">❌</span></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>WhatsApp booking button</strong></td>
              <td class="peek-col"><span class="check">✅</span></td>
              <td><span class="cross">❌</span></td>
              <td><span class="cross">❌</span></td>
              <td><span class="cross">❌</span></td>
              <td><span class="cross">❌</span></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>Open / Closed status</strong></td>
              <td class="peek-col"><span class="check">✅</span></td>
              <td><span class="cross">❌</span></td>
              <td><span class="cross">❌</span></td>
              <td><span class="cross">❌</span></td>
              <td><span class="cross">❌</span></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>QR code included</strong></td>
              <td class="peek-col"><span class="check">✅</span></td>
              <td><span class="cross">❌</span></td>
              <td><span class="cross">❌</span></td>
              <td><span class="cross">❌</span></td>
              <td><span class="cross">❌</span></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>Reviews section</strong></td>
              <td class="peek-col"><span class="check">✅</span></td>
              <td><span class="cross">❌</span></td>
              <td><span class="cross">❌</span></td>
              <td><span class="cross">❌</span></td>
              <td><span class="cross">❌</span></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>Maps embed</strong></td>
              <td class="peek-col"><span class="check">✅</span></td>
              <td><span class="check">✅</span></td>
              <td><span class="check">✅</span></td>
              <td><span class="cross">❌</span></td>
              <td><span class="check">✅</span></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>Multi-language (5 langs)</strong></td>
              <td class="peek-col"><span class="check">✅ <span style="color:var(--muted);font-size:0.8rem">DE ES PL HR EN</span></span></td>
              <td><span class="check">✅</span></td>
              <td><span class="check">✅</span></td>
              <td><span class="cross">❌</span></td>
              <td><span class="check">✅</span></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>Google index ready</strong></td>
              <td class="peek-col"><span class="check">✅</span></td>
              <td><span class="check">✅</span></td>
              <td><span class="check">✅</span></td>
              <td><span class="check">✅</span></td>
              <td><span class="check">✅</span></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>Email support</strong></td>
              <td class="peek-col"><span class="check">✅</span></td>
              <td><span class="check">✅</span></td>
              <td><span class="check">✅</span></td>
              <td><span class="cross">❌</span></td>
              <td><span class="check">✅</span></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>Custom domain</strong></td>
              <td class="peek-col"><span class="check">✅</span></td>
              <td><span class="check">✅</span></td>
              <td><span class="check">✅</span></td>
              <td><span class="check">✅</span></td>
              <td><span class="check">✅</span></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>No credit card needed</strong></td>
              <td class="peek-col"><span class="check">✅</span></td>
              <td><span class="cross">❌</span></td>
              <td><span class="cross">❌</span></td>
              <td><span class="check">✅</span></td>
              <td><span class="cross">❌</span></td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- UNIQUE ADVANTAGES -->
  <section class="advantages-section" id="advantages">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="advantages-header reveal">
        <div class="section-eyebrow">✦ Why Peek</div>
        <h2 class="section-title">What Makes Us<br/>Completely Different</h2>
        <p class="section-sub">Six things competitors simply can't offer — because they weren't built for local businesses from day one.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="adv-grid">
        <div class="adv-card reveal reveal-d1">
          <div class="adv-num">01</div>
          <h3>"We come to you"</h3>
          <p>You don't search for a builder and fill out a form. We find your business, generate a preview, and send it to you. No signup required to see what you'd get.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="adv-card reveal reveal-d2">
          <div class="adv-num">02</div>
          <h3>QR Code Included</h3>
          <p>Every page ships with a print-ready QR code. Put it on your menu, your business card, your shop window — your customers tap once and you're a click away.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="adv-card reveal reveal-d3">
          <div class="adv-num">03</div>
          <h3>WhatsApp Ready</h3>
          <p>A floating WhatsApp button puts your customers one tap away from booking, reserving, or asking a question. No forms. No waiting. Just real conversations.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="adv-card reveal reveal-d4">
          <div class="adv-num">04</div>
          <h3>Live Open Status</h3>
          <p>No more "are they even open?" phone calls. Peek shows your actual hours — and marks you open or closed in real time — so customers always know.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="adv-card reveal reveal-d1">
          <div class="adv-num">05</div>
          <h3>Real Reviews, Right There</h3>
          <p>Google and Yelp reviews displayed directly on your page — building credibility before your customer even calls or visits.</p>
        </div>
